data.description: $5,000 flooring credit being offered by seller! Charming Three Bedroom, Two Bath Home with POOL and Upgrades in Springhill. This spacious three-bedroom, two-bath gem boasts a two-car garage, NEW AC system, and recently installed attic steps for easy access. The kidney-shaped pool has been meticulously resurfaced and is surrounded by a COVERED LANAI, offering the perfect oasis for relaxation and entertaining. The heart of this home features a convenient pass-through window to the kitchen, allowing for seamless indoor and outdoor dining experiences. The kitchen is equipped with modern stainless steel appliances purchased in 2017, ensuring a stylish and functional cooking space. The adjacent dining room and family room both provide sliders that lead out to the pool area, seamlessly merging the indoors with the outdoors. The large laundry room includes a wash sink and ample storage space, making laundry a breeze. Some rooms have concrete floors, waiting for you to make it your own! Additionally, the living room and family room provide plenty of space for relaxation and gatherings. For added convenience and privacy, the property boasts a wood fence with gates on both sides, ensuring a secure and private environment. Animal enthusiasts will appreciate the included chicken coop, providing a space for your feathered friends. While this home offers numerous features and upgrades, the carpeting is ready for a refresh. With your personal touch, this home will truly shine. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to own a home with all the amenities you desire. Schedule a viewing today and envision your new life in this wonderful Springhill residence.
